ARGUMENT.

Wonderest thou, learned friend, what this sacrifice means on the Kalends of March, and Ι a bachelor? On this day I was delivered from death, and it shall be a holiday. Come, Maecenas, a hundred cups of my oldest wine to the health of thy friend. Away with anxiety. The Dacian has fallen, the Mede is divided against himself, the Oan- tabrian is in chains and the Scythian has unstrung his bow. Be here the private gentleman; never mind the people; enjoy thyself and unbend.
